  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Hard conversations are hard because they feel like they carry risk. Rejection, conflict, damage to the relationship. This sequence works with the feeling of risk rather than reasoning your way through it."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Setup"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Tap the karate chop point and repeat three times:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I dread this conversation and part of me wants to avoid it, I accept myself and what I'm feeling."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I'm not sure how this will go, I am willing to have it anyway."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I feel anxious about this, I trust that I can handle what comes."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Round one: name it"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Tap through the points (eyebrow, side of eye, under eye, under nose, chin, collarbone, under arm, top of head) while saying:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "This dread."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The pull to put it off again."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The fear of how they will react."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The fear of not handling it well."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "All of this weight before a conversation that hasn't happened yet."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Round two: shift"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I have had hard conversations before."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I know how to say difficult things."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I don't need it to go perfectly."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I can handle an uncomfortable response."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "This matters enough to say it."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I am ready enough."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where this practice comes from"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Original to homemade.education."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
